<p>These next couple of tabs are an in-depth look at Ad Astra Per Aspera's lore, intended to inform prospective writers and lore junkies about what the canon has to offer.</p>
<p>Bear in mind that <span class="h-span"><strong>none of this is required reading for the canon.</strong></span> If you only want to casually read the canon you can safely ignore this section (<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Misc.</span> tab may come in handy at times, though), unless you want a closer look at the canon's world.</p>
